{"type":"text","timestamp":1783744168911,"sessionID":"ses_0b0929e3affe1FHkKX9E1sdw9Y","part":{"id":"prt_f4f7000ef001UiuRkZkTFiwsnc","messageID":"msg_f4f6fd296001cffy19tXbYqWyk","sessionID":"ses_0b0929e3affe1FHkKX9E1sdw9Y","type":"text","text":"Initialization will create only the lineage-local control packet, with five evidence questions and a three-iteration convergence floor. The memory daemon timed out, so prior-context enrichment is non-blocking and the loop will use repository evidence directly, as the workflow permits.","time":{"start":1783744168175,"end":1783744168909},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0e800e67db5da1fb016a51c6a81f948191bc33fb31a11364fb","phase":"commentary"}}}}
