{"type":"text","timestamp":1783744560535,"sessionID":"ses_0b0929e3affe1FHkKX9E1sdw9Y","part":{"id":"prt_f4f75e106001JK3xg30zgQ2xeb","messageID":"msg_f4f75c97b001GFqQeJNbRrrbHd","sessionID":"ses_0b0929e3affe1FHkKX9E1sdw9Y","type":"text","text":"Iteration 2 passed the mechanical artifact gate and produced six exact OpenCode mappings. The third pass will now inspect checked-in Claude hook wiring and shared hook cores, then distinguish direct parity from runtime-specific approximations before evaluating whether legal convergence is possible.","time":{"start":1783744553222,"end":1783744560533},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0d39ffbb429655bb016a51c82936708191a5a2687aa80a6388","phase":"commentary"}}}}
