\"findingsCount\":7,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Seven distinct current-state findings established the baseline inventory, ownership boundaries, and four high-value automation families with no prior iteration evidence.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which skill contracts are plausible automation candidates?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Which skill contracts are plausible automation candidates?\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"generic prompt-context plugin\",\"hook-owned deep-loop convergence\"],\"toolsUsed\":[\"Glob\",\"Grep\",\"Read\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/plugins/README.md\",\".opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/skills/sk-code/code-quality/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/skills/sk-git/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/SKILL.md\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-11T04:34:00Z\",\"durationMs\":264000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gptsol-1783743995827-g7k8yl\",\"generation\":1,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast\",\"reasoningEffort\":null,\"serviceTier\":null}}\n3: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"run\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"newInfoRatio\":0.86,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"OpenCode plugin candidate mapping\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Six concrete OpenCode candidates and three eliminated variants were newly mapped; one candidate family partially reused the iteration-1 quality finding.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which OpenCode plugin hooks fit those candidates?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Which OpenCode plugin hooks fit those candidates?\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"full quality suite after every tool\",\"design-audit auto-scoring after edits\",\"blocking all mcp__ calls\"],\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/plugins/mk-deep-loop-guard.js\",\".opencode/plugins/mk-dist-freshness-guard.js