lineages/gptsol/research.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/research.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/research.md\n@@ -19,16 +19,41 @@\n | Post-Edit Quality Router | `sk-code/code-quality` | `tool.execute.after` + `experimental.chat.system.transform` | advisory, cheap checks |\n | External MCP Route Guard | `mcp-code-mode` | `tool.execute.before` | warn-first with native allowlist |\n | Completion Evidence Sentinel | `system-spec-kit`, `code-quality` | `session.idle` + `experimental.chat.system.transform` | advisory |\n | Session Readiness Primer | `system-spec-kit`, `system-skill-advisor` | `session.created` + `experimental.chat.system.transform` | advisory, one-shot |\n+| Incremental Code-Graph Freshness | `system-code-graph` | `tool.execute.after` | warm-only, debounced |\n \n+## Claude Candidate Set\n+\n+| Candidate | Skill grounding | Exact surface | Initial posture |\n+|---|---|---|---|\n+| Spec Mutation Gate | `system-spec-kit` | `UserPromptSubmit` + `PreToolUse/Write|Edit|Bash` | classify then enforce |\n+| Git Safety Guard | `sk-git` | `PreToolUse/Bash` | block exact destructive forms |\n+| Expanded Post-Edit Quality Router | `sk-code/code-quality` | `PostToolUse/Write|Edit` | extend existing warn-only hook |\n+| External MCP Route Guard | `mcp-code-mode` | `PreToolUse` external MCP matchers | manifest allowlist, warn-first |\n+| Completion Evidence Sentinel | `system-spec-kit`, `code-quality` | `Stop` | verify recorded evidence only |\n+| Incremental Code-Graph Freshness | `system-code-graph` | `PostToolUse/Write|Edit` | warm-only, debounced |\n+\n+## Priority Roadmap\n+\n+1. Git Safety Guard.\n+2. Spec Mutation Gate.\n+3. Expanded Post-Edit Quality Router.\n+4. Incremental Code-Graph Freshness.\n+5. Completion Evidence Sentinel.\n+6. External MCP Route Guard.\n+7. Session Readiness Primer.\n+\n ## Eliminated Alternatives\n \n - Another generic prompt-context injector.\n - Hook-owned deep-loop convergence or synthesis.\n - Full quality suites after every tool execution.\n - Design-audit auto-scoring without rendered evidence.\n - A blanket block on all `mcp__*` tools.\n+- Duplicate Claude PostToolUse or UserPromptSubmit registrations where an existing owner can be extended.\n+- SessionEnd completion verification and Stop-time test execution.\n+- Shared transport code across Claude and OpenCode; share policy cores only.\n \n ## Open Questions\n \n - Exact OpenCode and Claude hook mappings.\n","additions":25,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/prompts/iteration-003.md\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/iterations/iteration-003.md\nA .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/deltas/iter-003.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/deep-research-state.jsonl\nM .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/research.md","time":{"start":1783744679192,"end":1783744679199}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0614ca34a8d5a423016a51c8537f988191814ca239907597a9"}},"id":"prt_f4f768638001YH416sJ2b6VPvv","sessionID":"ses_0b0929e3affe1FHkKX9E1sdw9Y","messageID":"msg_f4f762a3c001tNIJGFcxGfQ0W2"}}
