ations: 3 / 5\n+- Questions answered: 5 / 5\n@@\n-- Minimum iteration floor: not reached (2 / 3)\n+- Minimum iteration floor: passed (3 / 3)\n+- Stop reason: converged (`all_questions_answered`)\n@@\n | 2 | OpenCode plugin candidate mapping | 0.86 | 6 | complete |\n+| 3 | Claude mapping and prioritization | 0.72 | 7 | complete |\n@@\n-- Ratios: `1.00 -> 0.86`\n-- Direction: descending, still high novelty\n+- Ratios: `1.00 -> 0.86 -> 0.72`\n+- Direction: descending; legal stop came from complete question coverage, not low novelty\n@@\n - Blanket `mcp__*` blocking.\n+- Duplicate Claude hook registrations.\n+- SessionEnd completion verification and Stop-time tests.\n+- Shared cross-runtime transport adapters.\n@@\n-Map equivalent Claude hooks, distinguish true parity from approximations, and rank the combined candidate set.\n+Synthesis complete; implementation planning should start with shared policy cores and runtime-specific adapters.\n@@\n - Fan-out override is not accepted by the stock reducer CLI, so workflow-owned reducer projections are refreshed directly inside this isolated lineage.\n+- Implementation-time smoke tests remain for matcher composition, Stop semantics, after-hook output, and graph debounce behavior.\n*** Update File: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/133-plugin-hook-opportunities/research/lineages/gptsol/deep-research-state.jsonl\n@@\n {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":3,\"run\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"newInfoRatio\":0.72,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Claude hook mapping and combined prioritization\",\"findingsCount\":7,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Six Claude mappings, one added cross-runtime code-graph candidate, a ranked roadmap, and five additional eliminations were new; the underlying candidate families partially reused earlier findings.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which Claude hooks 